= Examples =
;Default
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3}}

;Specify delimeter
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|delim=;}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|delim=;}}

;Specify conjunction
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|conj=&}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|conj=&}}

;Default (with an item containing <code>,</code>)
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2, extra|Item3}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2, extra|Item3}}
::'''''Explanation:''' when an item contains a comma (<code>,</code>), a semi-colon (<code>;</code>) is used as the default delimeter.''

;Specify delimeter (with an item containing <code>,</code>)
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2, extra|Item3|delim=,}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2, extra|Item3|delim=,}}
::'''''Explanation:''' the <code>delim=</code> parameter overrides the default delimeter, which in this case was a semi-colon (<code>;</code>).''

;Delimter override and no conjunction
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|delimOverride=<nowiki><nowiki></nowiki> + </nowiki>|noconj=true}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|delimoverride=<nowiki> + </nowiki>|noconj=true}}
::'''''Explanation:''' the <code>delimOverride=</code> parameter overrides the delimeter entirely, as it is concatenated with a space by default. The <code>noconj=</code> parameter specifies whether to include the conjunction before the final entry.''

;Final delimeter removal (Oxford comma, serial comma, series comma)
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|nolastdelim=true}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|nolastdelim=true}}

;"Linkify" items
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|link=true}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|Item1|Item2|Item3|link=true}}

{{---}}

;Empty
:<pre>{{Comma separated list|}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list|}}

:<pre>{{Comma separated list}}</pre>
:{{Comma separated list}}